author: elecharny
msg: Log a warning instead of an error when we try to store a value that is already present in an Attribute. That fixes DIRAPI-196

author: markt
msg: File.lastModified() has a resolution of 1s (1000ms). The last modified time has to be more than 1000ms ago to ensure that modifications that take place in the same second are not missed.
